all things will be improved in the world. To me, when I think about sort of the biggest issues in

00:05:23.320 --> 00:05:31.239
the world today, we're in the midst of a pandemic, we see emerging epidemics confronting us today,

00:05:32.200 --> 00:05:35.880
we're facing the real implications of climate change around the world,

00:05:36.839 --> 00:05:41.239
