00:06:39.799 --> 00:06:46.359
all about. But language doesn't know systems, language doesn't know the relationship between

00:06:46.359 --> 00:06:54.760
climate change and migration and food security. And we believe that by understanding how things

00:06:54.760 --> 00:06:59.959
are related, by elevating the relationships between things, and those being statistically

00:06:59.959 --> 00:07:06.920
based relationships, we can drive a more holistic understanding of problems in the world,

00:07:06.920 --> 00:07:10.679
of problems we face in business, of problems we face when we get a blood test result,

00:07:11.320 --> 00:07:17.239
really anywhere that we get data, we feel it's lacking context and the system around it. And so

00:07:17.239 --> 00:07:21.399
what we're really trying to do is build a technology that brings context, that brings

00:07:21.399 --> 00:07:26.119
that holistic view to any data point that we're looking at at any given moment supported.

00:07:27.320 --> 00:07:34.600
The final point is that we're a public benefit corporation, and our mission to relate everything,

00:07:34.600 --> 00:07:38.839
to help the world see and solve anything as a system is really what motivates us and our values

