as our core platform is really something that will be free and open and accessible to

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:07.079
researchers, professionals and the general public around the world.

00:08:09.239 --> 00:08:14.440
That's awesome. Thank you so much, Adam. And thanks for describing systems thinking a little

