about 50 people or so, 40-50 people. And yeah, my team at Spotify when I left was 300 or something

00:09:47.640 --> 00:09:55.400
like that. And now we're a 20-person startup, something like that. Honestly, there's so many

00:09:55.400 --> 00:10:02.919
upsides to both. It's incredible to be able to really start from first principles when you're

00:10:02.919 --> 00:10:10.359
building a team as we've done at System and emphasize values that are native to our culture

00:10:10.440 --> 00:10:19.320
and our mission. And then build a team that advances those values. And we can really think

