about all of that stuff foundationally in how we hire and how we design our ways of working.

00:10:26.359 --> 00:10:33.320
At the same time, our ambition for System is quite large. And we'd love to have 2000 people today

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:39.000
to be able to work on these problems. And so sometimes I wish I could take the same organization

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:43.719
at Spotify and be able to use that full, incredible brainpower and tech power to be

