build those kinds of education programs that continues today, sort of incredible team working

00:11:44.200 --> 00:11:54.919
on professional development and sort of growing data scientists at Spotify. Yeah. I think at the

00:11:54.919 --> 00:12:00.520
same time, like what unites it is I really believe in trying to identify what are the

00:12:01.159 --> 00:12:10.039
kind of primitives that allow teams, Spotify is a very strong, agile belief. And that really means

00:12:10.039 --> 00:12:16.039
kind of decentralization, federation of as much decision-making as possible to increase speed and

