that means, I think as a leader that you, I learned from Daniel Ack from the founder of Spotify,

00:12:27.719 --> 00:12:33.559
observing him do that, that it really puts a great deal of emphasis on what are the primitives

00:12:33.559 --> 00:12:38.840
that you feel are important for every leader in the company and then for their teams to really

