be agile, to be squads, to go off and do their thing. And so we put a great deal of emphasis

00:12:50.599 --> 00:12:57.400
at system on a set of first principles that govern how we think about the product and our technology

00:12:57.479 --> 00:13:04.280
and the tensions that shape any major decision. We put a great deal of emphasis on our values and

00:13:04.280 --> 00:13:09.239
talk a lot about those and use those as primitives when we're making product decisions or technology

00:13:09.239 --> 00:13:15.320
decisions. And we put a great deal of emphasis on sort of the use of data broadly in the company to

