Hmm, I think a lot about the values and culture of the company. Right. So at Spotify, I,

00:19:29.239 --> 00:19:36.439
you know, was an active participant in helping advance our values and advance our culture and

00:19:36.439 --> 00:19:43.079
hopefully, you know, positively contribute to it. But I inherited those values from a founder and

00:19:43.079 --> 00:19:48.839
a founding team. And those were his and their, you know, decisions about what's what is important

